n\n\r\nC: submit and hidden\n\r\nD: radio and checkbox'),(215,'Pergunta do dia: 1229','DjuxxnVvWUY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-30 08:54:28','Looking to the code below, what should be placed in the blank spot to run the code?\n\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\n// hello.php file\n\r\nnamespace myapp\\utils\\hello;\n\r\n\r\nclass Hello\n\r\n{\n\r\n    public static function world()\n\r\n    {\n\r\n        return \'This is SPARTA!!!\';\n\r\n    }\n\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n----------------------------------\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\n// myapp.php file\n\r\nnamespace myapp;\n\r\n\r\ninclude \'test.php\';\n\r\n\r\n__________________;\n\r\n\r\necho Hello::world();\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: use myapp\\utils\\hello\n\r\nB: use utils\\hello\\Hello\n\r\nC: use myapp\\utils\\hello\\Hello\n\r\nD: use utils\\hello\n\r\nE: use myapp\\utils\\hello\\Hello::world'),(216,'Pergunta do dia: 1230','zCyqz0AoE1g','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-30 08:49:21','Consider the following code snippet. Is this code acceptable from a security standpoint?\n\r\nAssume that the $action and $data variables are designed to be accepted from the user and \"register_globals\" is enabled.\n\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\nif(isUserAdmin()) { $isAdmin = true; }\n\r\n\r\n$data = validate_and_return_input($data);\n\r\n\r\nswitch($action){\n\r\n    case \'add\':\n\r\n        addSomething($data);\n\r\n        break;\n\r\n    case \'delete\':\n\r\n        if($isAdmin) {deleteSomething($data);}\n\r\n        break;\n\r\n    case \'edit\':\n\r\n        if($isAdmin) {editSomething($data);}\n\r\n        break;\n\r\n    default:\n\r\n        print “Bad Action.”;\n\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: Yes, it is secure. It checks for $isAdmin to be True before executing protected operations\n\r\nB: No, it is not secure because it doesn’t make sure $action is valid input\n\r\nC: No, it is not secure because $isAdmin can be hijacked by exploiting \"register_globals\"\n\r\nD: Yes, it is secure because it validates the user-data $data'),(217,'Pergunta do dia 1207','dj9s6iVQWQ0','Cyrille Grandval','2013-12-29 03:20:25','Tema : Formatos e tipos de dados\r\n\n\nPergunta : Which function is missing to complete the source code below, given the fact that myMethod and its parameters are defined in the WSDL file?\r\n\r\n\n\n&lt;?php\n$aParam = array(1, \'myParam\', \'Foo\');\n$rSoap = new SoapClient(\'myfile.wsdl\');\n$rSoap-&gt;..........(\'myMethod\', $aParam);\n\r\n\nAnswer :\na) call\nb) soapCall\nc) __soapCall\nd) _\ne) callback'),(218,'Pergunta do dia: 1228','U92HscUbVrI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-27 09:32:19','Is it possible to pass data from PHP to JavaScript?\n\r\n\r\nA: No, because PHP is server-side, and JavaScript is client-side.\n\r\nB: No, because PHP is a loosely typed language.\n\r\nC: Yes, because JavaScript executes before PHP.\n\r\nD: Yes, because PHP can generate valid JavaScript.'),(219,'Pergunta do dia: 1227','wWgihyv1XVk','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-27 04:16:54','Is it possible to pass data from JavaScript to PHP?\n\r\n\r\nA: Yes, but not without sending another HTTP request.\n\r\nB: Yes, because PHP executes before JavaScript.\n\r\nC: No, because JavaScript is server-side, and PHP is client-side.\n\r\nD: No, because JavaScript executes before PHP.'),(220,'Pergunta do dia: 1225','7QZgeT5bg24','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-26 01:29:57','Which of the following DBMSs do not have a native PHP extension?\n\r\n\r\nA: MySQL\n\r\nB: IBM DB/2\n\r\nC: PostgreSQL\n\r\nD: Microsoft SQL Server\n\r\nE: None of the above'),(221,'Pergunta do dia: 1226','1jI50CdF9kM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-26 12:26:23','Consider the following database table and query. Which of the indexes below will help speed up the process of executing the query?\n\r\n\r\nCREATE TABLE MYTABLE (\n\r\n    ID INT,\n\r\n    NAME VARCHAR (100),\n\r\n    ADDRESS1 VARCHAR (100),\n\r\n    ADDRESS2 VARCHAR (100),\n\r\n    ZIPCODE VARCHAR (10),\n\r\n    CITY VARCHAR (50),\n\r\n    PROVINCE VARCHAR (2)\n\r\n);\n\r\n\r\nSELECT ID, NAME\n\r\nFROM MYTABLE\n\r\nWHERE ID BETWEEN 0 AND 100\n\r\nORDER BY NAME, ZIPCODE\n\r\n\r\nA: Indexing the ID column\n\r\nB: Indexing the NAME and ADDRESS1 columns\n\r\nC: Indexing the ID column, and then the NAME and ZIPCODE columns separately\n\r\nD: Indexing the ZIPCODE and NAME columns\n\r\nE: Indexing the ZIPCODE column with a full-text index'),(222,'Pergunta do dia: 1224','tMKBgYGP8qM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-23 09:48:56','Assuming that the client browser is never restarted, how long after the last access will a session “expire” and be subject to garbage collection?\n\r\n\r\nA: After exactly 1,440 seconds\n\r\nB: After the number of seconds specified in the \"session.gc_maxlifetime\" INI setting\n\r\nC: It will never expire unless it is manually deleted\n\r\nD: It will only expire when the browser is restarted\n\r\nE: None of the above'),(223,'Pergunta do dia: 1223','iKBUGtE2CAA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-23 08:39:17','What happens when I execute the following code?\n\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\nnamespace Foo;\n\r\n\r\nfunction strlen() {}\n\r\nconst INI_ALL = 3;\n\r\n\r\n$a = strlen(\'hi\');\n\r\n$b = INI_ALL;\n\r\ntry\n\r\n{\n\r\n    if ($a == 2)\n\r\n        echo INI_ALL;\n\r\n    else\n\r\n        throw new Exception(\'error\');\n\r\n}\n\r\ncatch (Exception $e)\n\r\n{\n\r\n    echo $e-&gt;getMessage();\n\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: It will print \"3\"\n\r\nB: It will print \"error\"\n\r\nC: It will print \"7\"\n\r\nD: It will give an Fatal Error'),(224,'Pergunta do dia: 1222','RJ9ROh4LcAM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-22 09:46:45','By default, PHP stores session data in...\n\r\n\r\nA: The filesystem\n\r\nB: A database\n\r\nC: Virtual memory\n\r\nD: Shared memory\n\r\nE: None of the above'),(225,'pergunta','VsIDKSQe5l8','','2013-12-21 07:30:16','Descobri no linkedin (sem resposta)\r\n\r\n$a = \'One \';\n\r\n\n$b = \'Two\';\n\r\n\nif($a == $c)\n\r\n\n echo $a;\n\r\n\nif($b == $c)\n\r\n\n echo $b;\n\r\n\r\n\nwhich $c value gives the output \"OneTwo\"'),(226,'Pergunta do dia: 1209','6EPn90I0UnM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-20 08:26:22','What the following code will print out?\r\n\r\necho true ? \'a\' : true ? \'b\' : \'c\';\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de domingo (dia 08/12).'),(227,'Pergunta do dia: 1221','W4cW4EuhQfQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-20 11:04:24','Can we use the \"default\" keyword at any place in a \"switch\" statement? (Example below)\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$a = 12;\r\nswitch($a)\r\n{\r\n    default: echo \'YEAH\'; break;\r\n    case 12: echo \'TWELVE\'; break;\r\n\n\n    case 10: echo \'TEN\'; break;\r\n}\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: No! Only at the end of \"switch\" statement\r\nB: Yes! It goes where ever you want!\r\nC: No! It can be in the middle and the end, but not in the beginning'),(228,'Pergunta do dia: 1220','ta0nvqF5gN4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-20 08:44:18','What happens when a form submitted to a PHP script contains two elements with the same name?\n\r\n\r\nA: They are combined in an array and stored in the appropriate superglobal array B: The value of the second element is added to the value of the first in the appropriate superglobal array\n\r\nC: The value of the second element overwrites the value of the first in the appropriate superglobal array\n\r\nD: The second element is automatically renamed\n\r\nE: PHP outputs a warning'),(229,'Pergunta do dia: 1213','zTyOYxUJjRE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-18 06:47:13','Consider the following script. What line of code should be inserted in the marked location in order to display the string \"php\" when this script is executed?\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$alpha = \'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz\';\r\n\n$letters = array(15, 7, 15);\r\nforeach($letters as $val) {\r\n    /* What should be here */\r\n}\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: echo chr($val);\r\nB: echo asc($val);\r\nC: echo substr($alpha, $val, 2);\r\nD: echo $alpha{$val};\r\nE: echo $alpha{$val+1};\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 12/12).'),(230,'Pergunta do dia: 1219','V-C88ieHeGw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-18 12:53:18','Consider the following form and subsequent script. What will the script print out if the user types the word \"php\" and \"great\" in the two text boxes respectively?\n\r\n\r\n&lt;form action=\"index.php\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n\r\n&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"element[]\"&gt;\n\r\n&lt;input type=\"text\" name=\"element[]\"&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\n\r\n\r\n// index.php\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\necho $_GET[\'element\'];\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: Nothing\n\r\nB: Array\n\r\nC: A Notice\n\r\nD: phpgreat\n\r\nE: greatphp'),(231,'Pergunta do dia: 1218','aPiHa8cja44','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-17 11:40:35','If no expiration time is explicitly set for a cookie, what happens to it?\n\r\n\r\nA: It expires right away\n\r\nB: It never expires\n\r\nC: It is not set\n\r\nD: It expires at the end of the user’s browser session\n\r\nE: It expires only if the script doesn’t create a server-side session'),(232,'Pergunta do dia: 1214','BI4FU8r9QW4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-17 11:06:06','Which of the following PCRE regular expressions best matches the string php|conference?\r\n\r\nA: .*\r\nB: ...|..........\r\nC: \\d{3}\\|\\d{10}\r\nD: [az]{3}\\|[az]{10}\r\nE: [a-z][a-z][a-z]\\|\\w{10}\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de sexta-feira (dia 13/12).'),(233,'Pergunta do dia: 1210','KNVELt6ajWs','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-17 08:08:39','What is displayed when the following script is executed?\r\n&lt;?php\r\ndefine(\'myvalue\', \"10\");\r\n\r\n$myarray[10] = \"Dog\";\r\n$myarray[] = \"Human\";\r\n$myarray[\'myvalue\'] = \"Cat\";\r\n\n$myarray[\"Dog\"] = \"Cat\";\r\n\r\nprint \"The value is: \";\r\nprint $myarray[myvalue].\"\\n\";\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: The value is: Dog\r\nB: The value is: Cat\r\nC: The value is: Human\r\nD: The value is: 10\r\n\nE: A parse error occurs\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de segunda-feira (dia 09/12).'),(234,'Pergunta do dia: 1217','r_ckj3SK41w','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-17 08:06:57','What happens if you add a string to an integer using the + operator?\r\n\r\nA: The interpreter outputs a type mismatch error\r\nB: The string is converted to a number and added to the integer \r\nC: The string is discarded and the integer is preserved\r\n\nD: The integer and string are concatenated together in a new string\r\nE: The integer is discarded and the string is preserved'),(235,'Pergunta do dia: 1211','PC8VF6c0ujg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-16 07:30:27','Considering the following segment of code, what should go in the marked segment to produce the following array output?\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\ndefine(\"STOP_AT\", 1024);\r\n\r\n$result = array();\r\n\r\n/* Missing code */\r\n{\r\n    $result[] = $idx;\r\n}\r\n\r\nprint_r($result);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\n// Output\r\nArray{\r\n    [0] =&gt; 1,\r\n    [1] =&gt; 2, \r\n    [2] =&gt; 4,\r\n    [3] =&gt; 8,\r\n    [4] =&gt; 16,\r\n\n    [5] =&gt; 32,\r\n    [6] =&gt; 64,\r\n    [7] =&gt; 128,\r\n    [8] =&gt; 256,\r\n    [9] =&gt; 512\r\n}\r\n\r\nA: foreach($result as $key =&gt; $val)\r\nB: while($idx *= 2)\r\nC: for($idx = 1; $idx &lt; STOP_AT; $idx *= 2)\r\n\nD: for($idx *= 2; STOP_AT &gt;= $idx; $idx = 0)\r\nE: while($idx &lt; STOP_AT) do $idx *= 2\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de terça-feira (dia 10/12).'),(236,'Pergunta do dia: 1212','cdbv_skoV4c','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-16 06:32:12','In what order will the following script output the contents of the $array array?\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$array = array (\'a1\', \'a3\', \'a5\', \'a10\', \'a20\');\r\nnatsort ($array);\r\n\nvar_dump ($array);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: a1, a3, a5, a10, a20\r\nB: a1, a20, a3, a5, a10\r\nC: a10, a1, a20, a3, a5\r\nD: a1, a10, a5, a20, a3\r\nE: a1, a10, a20, a3, a5\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quarta-feira (dia 11/12).'),(237,'Pergunta do dia: 1215','hvJ7yh6eSOI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-16 06:26:45','What will be the output of the following script?\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$s = \'12345\';\r\n$s[$s[1]] = \'2\';\r\necho $s;\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: 12345\r\nB: 12245\r\nC: 22345\r\nD: 11345\r\nE: Array\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de sábado (dia 14/12).'),(238,'Pergunta do dia: 1216','rLratT5tl1g','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-16 03:54:07','Which of the strings below will be matched by the following PCRE regular expression?\r\n(Choose 2)\r\n\r\n/.*\\*123\\d/\r\n\r\nA: ******123\r\nB: *****_1234\r\nC: ******1234\r\nD: _*1234\r\nE: _*123\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo (dia 15/12).'),(239,'Pergunta do dia: 1208','zYxOm6bT2zI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-16 02:57:51','What is the output of the following code?\r\n&lt;?php \r\nfunction pears(Array $pears)\r\n{\r\n    if (count($pears) &gt; 0)\r\n    {\r\n        echo array_pop($pears);\r\n        pears($pears);\r\n    }\r\n\n}\r\n\r\n$fruit = array(\"PHP\", \"Conference\");\r\npears($fruit);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: ConferencePHP\r\nB: PHP Conference\r\nC: Conference PHP\r\nD: Conference\r\nE: Conference PHP\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de sábado (dia 07/12).'),(240,'Pergunta prática #1','caUq67ZRgXk','Cyrille Grandval','2013-12-12 02:51:06','Ola,\r\n\nEu tenho um \"falso\" problema (porque já sei a resposta ;-)). Vocês devem saber que por padrão esse código em um arquivo (por exemplo index.php), chamado diretamente, pode levar um erro : Warning: Cannot modify header information - headers already sent by (output started at .....\n\r\n\n&lt;?php\nprint \"Bom dia !\";\nheader(\"Location: login.php\");\n\r\n\nMas não tenho erro no meu sistema. Alguém tem uma ideia de porque não tenho um erro ? '),(241,'Pergunta do dia: 1194','M_ccoZ4WZ38','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-12 10:21:59','Celina works as a Database Administrator for Tech Mart Inc. The company uses an Oracle database. The database contains a table named Employees. Following is the structure of the table:\n\r\n\r\nEmpID NUMBER (5) PRIMARY KEY\n\r\nEmpName VARCHAR2 (35) NOT NULL\n\r\nSalary NUMBER (9, 2) NOT NULL\n\r\nCommission NUMBER (4, 2)\n\r\nManagerName VARCHAR2 (25)\n\r\nManagerID NUMBER (5)\n\r\n\r\nCelina wants to display the names of employees and their managers, using a self join. Which of the following SQL statements will she use to accomplish this?\n\r\n\r\nA: SELECT e.EmpName, m.ManagerName FROM Employees e INNER JOIN Employees m ON e.EmpID = m.ManagerID;\n\r\n\r\nB: SELECT e.EmpName, m.ManagerName FROM Employees e, Employees m WHERE e.EmpID = m.ManagerID;\n\r\n\r\nC: SELECT e.EmpName, m.ManagerName FROM Employees e LEFT OUTER JOIN Employees m ON e.EmpID = m.ManagerID;\n\r\n\r\nD: SELECT e.EmpName, m.ManagerName FROM Employees e SELF JOIN Employees m ON e.EmpID = m.ManagerID;'),(242,'Pergunta do dia 1206','apEjzaGlwU0','Cyrille Grandval','2013-12-10 09:58:11','Tema : Formatos e tipos de dadosPergunta : What is the result when running the code above?\n\r\n\n&lt;?php\n\r\n\n$sXml = \'&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\n  &lt;configenv&gt;\n    &lt;production&gt;\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"3\" /&gt;\n    &lt;/production&gt;\n    &lt;staging&gt;\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"10\" /&gt;\r\n\n\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"7\" /&gt;\r\n\n\n    &lt;/staging&gt;\n    &lt;testing&gt;\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"1\" /&gt;\r\n\n\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"20\" /&gt;\r\n\n\n    &lt;/testing&gt;\n  &lt;/configenv&gt;\';\n\r\n\n$oXmlElement = new SimpleXmlElement($sXml);\n$b = $oXmlElement-&gt;xpath(\'*/acl[@id &gt; 7]\');\n\r\n\nAnswers :\na) The xml isn\'t correct and an exception will be thrown\nb) $b is an array containing 2 SimpleXml objects representing the acl tags for which the value of the attribute id is bigger than 7\nc) The xpath expression isn\'t correct and an exception will be thrown\nd) $b is equal to null\ne) $b is a xml above : \n\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\n  &lt;configenv&gt;\n    &lt;production&gt;&lt;/production&gt;\n    &lt;staging&gt;\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"10\" /&gt;\n    &lt;/staging&gt;\n    &lt;testing&gt;\n        &lt;acl name=\"userTest\" id=\"20\" /&gt;\r\n\n\n    &lt;/testing&gt;\n  &lt;/configenv&gt;'),(243,'Pergunta do dia: 1201 (direto da PHP Conference 2013)','DL6e3wj9pqg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-12-06 07:49:18','Which of the following is not an advantage of encapsulation?\n\r\n\r\nA: It provides code reusability.\n\r\nB: It provides code security.\n\r\nC: Data can be accessed only by calling methods.\n\r\nD: It provides code flexibility by allowing access of data to other code outside the packa-ge.'),(244,'Pergunta do dia 1204','02-YiPvY3Ec','Cyrille Grandval','2013-12-06 07:44:09','Tema : PHP Básico\n\r\n\n$a = \'myVar\';\n\r\n\nswitch ($a) {\n  case 0:\n  	echo \'case 0\';\n	\n  case \'myVar\':\n  	echo \'case myVar\';\n\r\n\n  case \'nothing\':\n  	echo \'case nothing\';\n}\n\r\n\nAnswer : \n___________________'),(245,'Pergunta do dia 1205','yowlw5m3fRQ','Cyrille Grandval','2013-12-06 02:11:15','Tema : Formatos e tipos de dadosPergunta : What method is used to set the time in the DateTime class ?'),(246,'Pergunta do dia 1202','hB2QYa4d65c','Cyrille Grandval','2013-12-05 11:29:23','Tema : PHP BásicoPergunta : What is the output of the following script ?\n\r\n&lt;?php \r\n$i = 4; \r\necho $i &gt;&gt; 2; \r\n\r\n$i = 4; \r\necho $i &gt;&gt; 3; \r\n\r\n$i = 4; \r\necho $i &gt;&gt; 4;'),(247,'Pergunta do Dia 1203','RO_5IOiDHkk','Flávio Ferreira','2013-12-03 09:59:26','Uma das Questões que cairam na minha prova Z.C.E envolvia a função preg_split. Não me lembro totalmente dela, mas formulei uma parecida. \r\n\r\nHow many elements have a variable $matches the end of the script?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$matches = preg_split(\'/(\\s)/\', \'1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8\', -1 ,PREG_SPLIT_DELIM_CAPTURE ); \nvar_dump($matches);\r\n\n?&gt;\n\n\r\nA) 0\r\nB) 8\r\nC) 7\r\nD) 15\r\n\r\nSempre que me lembrar de algo, postarei aqui pra ajudar a galera. '),(248,'Pergunta do dia: 1200 (direto da PHP Conference 2013)','Vzp6ywaYx0k','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-29 05:46:25','Identify whether the given statement is true or false.\n\r\n“A Cartesian product is generated when a join between two or more tables is defined without specifying any join condition.”\n\r\n\r\nA: True\n\r\nB: False'),(249,'Pergunta do dia: 1199 (pergunta comemorativa da PHP Conference 2013)','GZ4z4iPqnqw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-28 10:58:49','Identify whether the given statement is true or false.\n\r\n\"The IN operator cannot be used in a condition that involves an outer join.\"\n\r\n\r\nA: True\n\r\nB: False'),(250,'Pergunta do dia: 1198','UJtc6kFXmjY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-27 11:00:46','Which of the following joins returns all rows from the left and right tables in a join expression even if the data values in the joined columns do not match?\r\n\r\nA: CROSS JOIN\r\nB: INNER JOIN\r\nC: FULL OUTER JOIN\r\n\n\nD: RIGHT OUTER JOIN\r\nE: LEFT OUTER JOIN'),(251,'Pergunta do dia: 1182','fe2qPhAbPYw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-26 09:15:51','What will be the output of the following code snippet?\r\n&lt;?php\r\necho \'hello \' . 1 + 2 . \'34\';\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: 0\r\nB: hello1234\r\nC: hello334\r\nD: 234\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de segunda-feira (dia 11/11).'),(252,'Pergunta do dia: 1197','yD25NL5zin4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-26 05:22:21','Which of the following joins is used to join a table to itself?\r\n\r\nA: Self join\r\nB: Non-equijoin\r\nC: Outer join\r\nD: Equijoin\r\nE: Cross join\r\nF: Left outer join'),(253,'Pergunta do dia: 1180','OAffUJa8Yyw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 05:15:17','What will be the output of the following code snippet?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$my_array = array(1 =&gt; \'a\', 2 =&gt; \'b\');\r\nprint_r($my_array);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: Array ([1] =&gt; a [2] =&gt; b)\r\n\nB: bool(true)\r\nC: It will show a blank screen.\r\nD: It will show an error message.\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de sábado (dia 09/11).'),(254,'Pergunta do dia: 1181','pCTBzjdG3Hs','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 05:14:52','What will be the output of the following PHP code snippet?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$array = array (1.1 =&gt; \'1\', 1.2 =&gt; \'1\');\r\necho count ($array);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: 1\r\nB: 2\r\nC: 0\r\nD: The script will throw an error message.\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de domingo (dia 10/11).'),(255,'Pergunta do dia: 1191','7h_HHGgKc8w','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 05:12:30','In which of the following ways will you send data from a Web page if you do not know how data is sent?\r\n\r\nA: $_POST[]\r\nB: $_GET[]\r\nC: $_REQUEST[]\r\nD: $_SEND[]\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, quarta-feira (dia 20/11).'),(256,'Pergunta do dia: 1173','_70JwPxVQbs','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 05:03:33','What will be the output of the following script?\r\n&lt;?php\r\nclass foo {\r\nconst BAR = \"Hello PHP\"; }\r\necho foo::BAR;\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: Hello PHP\r\nB: 0\r\nC: Null\r\nD: The PHP script will show an error message.\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de sábado (dia 02/11).'),(257,'Pergunta do dia: 1175','zX2LUPF1C_o','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 04:59:44','You have been given the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$xmlstring = &lt;&lt;&lt;XML\r\n&lt;?xml version=“1.0” encoding=“ISO-8859-1”?&gt;\r\n&lt;email&gt;\r\n&lt;to&gt;je...@ucertify.com&lt;/to&gt;\r\n\n&lt;from&gt;jo...@ucertify.com&lt;/from&gt;\r\n&lt;heading&gt;Technical issue in Linux OS&lt;/heading&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;There is a technical issue in my Linux system. Please Fix it. &lt;/body&gt; &lt;/email&gt;\r\n\nXML;\r\n$xml = new SimpleXMLElement($xmlstring);\r\nforeach($xml-&gt;children() as $child) {\r\n&lt;Insert code here.&gt;\r\n}\r\nWhich of the following code snippets will you insert at line number 13 to get the following output?\r\n\nto: je...@ucertify.com\r\nfrom: jo...@ucertify.com\r\nheading: Technical issue in Linux OS\r\nbody: There is a technical issue in my Linux system. please Fix it.\r\n\r\nA: echo $child-&gt;getName() . \": \" . $child . \"&lt;br /&gt;\";\r\nB: echo $child-&gt;getNamespaces() . \": \" . $child . \"&lt;br /&gt;\";\r\nC: echo $child-&gt;getDocNamespaces() . \": \" . $child . \"&lt;br /&gt;\";\r\n\nD: echo $child-&gt;asXML() . \": \" . $child . \"&lt;br /&gt;\";\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de segunda-feira (dia 04/11).'),(258,'Pergunta do dia: 1196','QS9HMq3v2M8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 04:55:19','Identify whether the given statement is true or false.\r\nAll group functions except COUNT (*) and GROUPING ignore NULL values.\r\n\r\nA: True\r\nB: False'),(259,'Pergunta do dia: 1185','y1x5ZTUbqE8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 04:53:47','Which of the following functions will you use to break a string into an array based on a specific pattern?\r\n\r\nA: preg_split()\r\nB: explode()\r\nC: implode()\r\nD: strstr()\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 14/11).'),(260,'Pergunta do dia: 1195','5vKKypXVqqo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 10:06:06','You work as a Database Administrator for Dolliver Inc. The company uses an Oracle database. The database contains two tables, named Employees and Departments. You want to retrieve all matched and unmatched rows from both the tables. Which of the following types of joins will you use to accomplish this?\n\r\n\r\nA: LEFT OUTER JOIN\n\r\nB: CROSS JOIN\n\r\nC: RIGHT OUTER JOIN\n\r\nD: FULL OUTER JOIN'),(261,'Pergunta do dia: 1183','_UalOjGqjc4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-25 09:10:34','Which of the following functions can be used to compare two strings using a case-insensitive binary algorithm?\r\n\r\nA: strcasecmp()\r\nB: strcmp()\r\nC: strstr()\r\nD: substr()\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de terça-feira (dia 12/11).'),(262,'Pergunta do dia: 1193','S6K_ns5uYhY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-11-22 06:16:11','Symonds works as a Database Administrator for Blue Well Inc. The company uses an Oracle database. The database contains a table named Employees. Following is the structure of the table:\r\n\r\nEmployeeID NUMBER (5) PRIMARY KEY\r\n\nEmployeeName VARCHAR2 (35) NOT NULL\r\nSalary NUMBER (9, 2) NOT NULL\r\nCommission NUMBER (4, 2)\r\nDepartmentID NUMBER (5)\r\n\r\nSymonds queries the Employees table with the follow