\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\nWhat will be the output?\n\r\n\r\nA: d e f\n\r\nB: c d e\n\r\nC: b c d\n\r\nD: a b c'),(380,'Pergunta do dia: 1084','AOW9HSOm8wc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-10 12:55:55','Which of the following functions can be used as a countermeasure to a Shell Injection attack?\r\n\r\nA: escapeshellarg()\r\nB: escapeshellcmd()\r\nC: mysql_real_escape_string()\r\nD: regenerateid()'),(381,'Pergunta do dia: 1083','W_OD7xU2mZA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-09 10:47:02','Consider the PHP program (which includes a file specified by request):\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\n$color = \'blue\';\n\r\nif (isset( $_GET[\'COLOR\'] ) )\n\r\n$color = $_GET[\'COLOR\'];\n\r\nrequire( $color . \'.php\' );\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n&lt;hr width=50%&gt;\n\r\n&lt;form method=“get”&gt;\n\r\n&lt;select name=“COLOR”&gt;\n\r\n&lt;option value=“red”&gt;red&lt;/option&gt;\n\r\n&lt;option value=“blue”&gt;blue&lt;/option&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/select&gt;\n\r\n&lt;input type=“submit”&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA malicious user injects the following command:\n\r\n/vulnerable.php?COLOR=C:\\\\notes.txt\n\r\nwhere vulnerable.php is a remotely hosted file containing an exploit.\n\r\nWhat does the malicious user want to do?\n\r\n\r\nA: Remove the .php suffix, allowing access to files other than .php.\n\r\nB: Execute the malicious code that exists in the file vulnerable.php.\n\r\nC: Perform a cross-site scripting attack.\n\r\nD: Inject a remotely hosted file containing an exploit.'),(382,'Pergunta do dia: 1082','o-AOCA0zGbk','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-08 11:32:50','Consider the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$a = 5;\r\n$b = 10;\r\nfunction Mul() {\r\n**********************\r\n}\r\nMul();\r\nprint($b);\r\n?&gt;\r\nWhat can you write instead of ****** on line 5 to get the output 50?\r\n\r\nA:\r\n$GLOBALS[\'b\'] = $GLOBALS[\'a\'] * $GLOBALS[\'b\'];\r\n\r\nB:\r\nglobal $a, $b;\r\n$b = $a * $b;\r\n\r\nC:\r\nglobals($b = $a * $b);\r\n\r\nD:\r\n$b = $a * $b;'),(383,'Pergunta do dia : 1025','_YFZAZjbLxU','Cyrille Grandval','2013-08-07 04:51:39','Which parsing model enable event-based XML parsing?\r\n\r\n\nA) DOM\nB) XPath\nC) XML Object Mapping\n\nD) SAX'),(384,'Pergunta do dia: 912','mxQJGMMRp2M','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-06 11:25:05','The _________ function is great for monitoring a series of streams to\n\r\ndetermine when one or more of them will not block a particular type of\n\r\nstream operation.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 14/02).'),(385,'Pergunta do dia: 1078','K31eA_gfCcY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-05 08:37:01','You work as a Web Developer for Remote Inc. What will be the output when you try to run the script below?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$b = false;\r\nif($b = true)\r\nprint(“true”);\r\nelse\r\nprint(“false”);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nA: true\r\nB: false\r\nC: true false\r\nD: The script will throw an error message.\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de terça-feira (dia 30/07).'),(386,'Pergunta do dia: 1079','0Ek9Y4UnCL8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-05 08:36:28','You run the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\nfor($x = 1; $x &lt;= 2; $x++){\r\n    for($y = 1; $y &lt;= 3; $y++){\r\n        if ($x == $y) continue;\r\n        print(“x = $x y = $y&lt;br&gt;“);\r\n        }\r\n\n    }\r\n?&gt;\r\nWhat will be the output?\r\nA: x = 1 y = 1\r\nB: x = 1 y = 2\r\nC: x = 1 y = 3\r\nD: x = 2 y = 1\r\nE: x = 2 y = 2\r\nF: x = 2 y = 3\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quarta-feira (dia 31/07).'),(387,'Pergunta do dia: 1080','8xnPYAjPiuE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-05 08:35:45','You want to create an anonymous function in the middle of a script that will return the square of a given number. Which of the following PHP scripts can you use to accomplish the task?\r\nA:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n\n$foo = create_function(\'$x\', \'return $x*$x;\');\r\necho $foo(10);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nB:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$foo = create_function(\"\\$x\", \"return \\$x*\\$x;\");\r\necho $foo(10);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nC:\r\n\n&lt;?php\r\n$foo = create_function(\"$x\", \"return $x*$x;\");\r\necho $foo(10);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\nD:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$foo = create_function(\"$x\", \"$x*$x;\");\r\necho $foo(10);\r\n?&gt;\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira (dia 01/08).'),(388,'Pergunta do dia: 1081','BqbegXDSfGA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-05 08:35:15','Consider the following PHP script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$a = 5;\r\n$b = 10;\r\nfunction Mul()\r\n{\r\n$a =0;\r\n$b = $a * $b;\r\n}\r\nMul();\r\nprint($b);\r\n?&gt;\r\nWhat will be the output of the above script?\r\n\nA: 50\r\nB: 10\r\nC: 0\r\nD: The script will return an error message.\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, sexta-feira (dia 02/08).'),(389,'Pergunta do dia: 1069','GtkBdeWpx5g','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-05 10:58:37','Which of the following is a valid parameter of the flock() function that allows other processes to read a file but prevents from writing anything?\r\n\r\nA: LOCK_SH\r\nB: LOCK_UN\r\nC: LOCK_EX\r\nD: LOCK_RW'),(390,'Pergunta do dia: 1077','OYXPkn_f-XI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-05 02:00:38','Fred works as a Web developer in Fastech Inc. He writes the following script:\r\n&lt;?php\r\n$s = 2;\r\nswitch ($s) {\r\ncase 1: print(“Fred”);\r\nbreak; case 2: print(“Fast”); case 3: print(“Tech”);\r\n\ndefault: print(“default”);\r\n\n}\r\n\r\nWhat will be displayed as output when Fred attempts to run this PHP script?\r\n\r\nA: Fast\r\nB: Fast Tech default\r\nC: Fast Tech\r\nD: default\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, segunda-feira (dia 29/07).'),(391,'Pergunta do dia: 1076','piL7Qfy1XaM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-03 12:43:44','Mark works as a Web Developer for Unicorn Inc. He develops an application in PHP using the following code:\r\n&lt;?php\r\nswitch(1) {\r\ncase 1: print(“Book Details&lt;br&gt;“);\r\ncase 2: print(“Book Author&lt;br&gt;“);\r\n\n\ndefault: print(“Missing Book&lt;br&gt;“);\r\n}\r\n?&gt;\r\nWhat will be the output of the script?\r\n\r\nA: Book Details\r\nB: Book Author\r\nC: Missing Book\r\nD: It will display all the three lines.\r\nE: The script will throw an error.\r\n\r\n\nOb