s that a request was successful and the requested data will follow?\r\n\r\nA: 200\r\nB: 301\r\nC: 302\r\nD: 404\r\n\r\n\nObs.: pergunta de segunda-feira passada (dia 22/07).'),(398,'Pergunta do dia: 1068','70KMnP9TbT4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-03 12:39:41','Which of the following is a valid PHP function that is used to delete a file using PHP?\r\n\r\nA: unlink()\r\nB: del()\r\nC: remove()\r\nD: unset()'),(399,'Pergunta do dia: 1067','kHLaX_9NEqQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-03 12:39:20','Which of the following functions will you use to change the access and modification time of a file?\r\n\r\nA: touch\r\nB: chown\r\nC: chgrp\r\nD: chmod'),(400,'Pergunta do dia: 1066','1Be8X-b0Aug','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-03 12:38:54','Which of the following functions will you use to create an empty file?\r\n\r\nA: touch\r\nB: cd\r\nC: chown\r\nD: chgrp'),(401,'Pergunta do dia: 1065','HCuZb3Daa8k','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-03 12:38:31','A table named employees is given below:\r\n\n(imagem em anexo)\r\nWhich of the following statements would return the employees names, in ascending order, based on their last name and first name?\r\n\r\nA: select fname, lname from employees group by lname\r\nB: select fname, lname from employees order by lname desc\r\nC: select fname, lname from employees order by lname asc\r\nD: select fname, lname from employees order by lname'),(402,'Pergunta do dia: 1062','LJaE7z1ZYRM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-08-03 12:35:39','You have the following code in the welcome.html file:\n\r\n&lt;form action=“welcome.php” method=“post”&gt;\n\r\nYour Name: &lt;input type=“text” name=“fname” /&gt;\n\r\nYour Girl Friend Name: &lt;input type=“text” name=“fname” /&gt;\n\r\n&lt;input type=“submit” /&gt;\n\r\n&lt;/form&gt;\n\r\nThe PHP code of the welcome.php file is as follows:\n\r\nWelcome &lt;?php echo $_POST[“fname”];?&gt; and &lt;?php echo $_POST[“fname”];?&gt;!\n\r\nWhat will be the output if you give your name as John and your girlfriend\'