o stringrev($string1);\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nD:\n\r\n&lt;?php $string1= \"ZeNd php\";\n\r\n$string1= str_to_lower($string1);\n\r\necho strev($string1);\n\r\n?&gt;'),(514,'Pergunta do dia: 949','V8rekra9_No','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-26 07:15:24','Mark works as a Web developer for InfoTech Inc. He develops a program\n\r\nthat uses a class named Shape. However, the class Shape defines two\n\r\nmethods with the same name in the same class. Which of the following\n\r\nstatements are true about the above scenario?\n\r\n\r\nA: This feature is not allowed in PHP.\n\r\nB: This feature is known as method overloading.\n\r\nC: This feature is known as method overriding.\n\r\nD: This feature is known as autoloading.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sábado (dia 23/03).'),(515,'Pergunta do dia: 948','L_nwLGQ2ufM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-26 01:55:24','Which of the following scripts should you run to get the output given below?\n\r\n\"($a+$b)\"\n\r\n\r\nA: &lt;?php echo \"\\\"{\\$a+\\$b}\\\"; ?&gt;\n\r\nB: &lt;?php echo &lt;&lt;&lt;TEXT \"$a+$b\" TEXT; ?&gt;\n\r\nC: &lt;?php echo \"\\{\\$a+\\$b}\\\"; ?&gt;\n\r\nD: &lt;?php echo \"{\\$a+\\$b}\"; ?&gt;'),(516,'Pergunta do dia: 950','cWgZyY7XlK4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-26 12:45:29','Which of the following statements are true about access control modifiers?\n\r\n(checkbox)\n\r\n\r\nA: A variable declared as private can be accessed only by code within\n\r\nthe same class.\n\r\nB: For using the abstract function or method, a user must have to\n\r\ninherit the abstract function or method first.\n\r\nC: A variable declared as protected can be accessed by any subclass of\n\r\nthe class in which the variable is declared.\n\r\nD: The final variable or function can be overridden in an inherited class.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo (dia 24/03).'),(517,'Pergunta do dia: 951','WITtrya3uWE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-26 09:25:40','Maria creates an application using PHP script. The application\n\r\ncontains certain classes. The class design requires that a particular\n\r\nmember variable must be directly accessible to any subclass of this\n\r\nclass. What should Maria do to achieve this?\n\r\n\r\nA: Mark the variable as public.\n\r\nB: Mark the variable as private.\n\r\nC: Mark the variable as protected.\n\r\nD: Mark the variable as final.'),(518,'Pergunta do dia: 947','zPeJXNSku_Y','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-22 09:34:31','You passed an associative array to the sort() function. What will happen?\n\r\n\r\nA: The key of the array will be sorted and the elements will not be\n\r\nsorted, however, they will be preserved.\n\r\nB: The elements of the array will be sorted and the keys will not be\n\r\nsorted, however, they will be preserved.\n\r\nC: The elements of the array will be sorted and keys will not be preserved.\n\r\nD: The keys will be sorted, however, elements will not be preserved.'),(519,'Pergunta do dia: 946','OgrnMjUbcW8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-21 02:50:35','Fill in the blank with the appropriate PHP function.\n\r\nThe __________ function is used to replace the current session id with\n\r\nthe new session id, and to keep information of the current session.\n\r\nThis function is used as a countermeasure to a session fixation attack\n\r\nin which the attacker attempts to exploit the vulnerability of a\n\r\nsystem by fixating another person\'s session identifier (SID).'),(520,'Pergunta do dia: 945','EQVYzIVQbK4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-20 11:22:20','Which of the following operators has the highest precedence order?\n\r\n\r\nA: [\n\r\nB: ++\n\r\nC: -\n\r\nD: --'),(521,'Pergunta do dia: 934','IyR-RS4o4iU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2013-03-19 11:51:56','John works as a Website Developer for PHPWEB Inc. He is using a\n\r\nWindows operating system and is also working on PHP engine 5.0. He\n\r\ndevelops the following script:\n\r\n&lt;?php echo date(\"M-d-Y\", mktime(0, 0, 0, 12, 32, 1965)); ?&gt;\n\r\nWhat will be the output of the above PHP script?\"\