pleXML is harder to use but has\n\r\nbasic functionality while DOM has power and flexibility.\n\r\nC: The main difference is that SimpleXML is easier to use but has more\n\r\nadvanced functionality while DOM has power and flexibility.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira, dia 1/11.'),(670,'Pergunta do dia: 808','ZYyjmszR0cA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-11-05 01:31:18','What is the SOAP web service used for\n\r\n\r\nA: XML and SOAP are tied together as all the message sent to a SOAP\n\r\nserver are sent in what is called a SOAP envelope that is used as an\n\r\nXML wrapper for dataread and generated.\n\r\nB: XML and SOAP are tied together as all the message sent to and from\n\r\na SOAP server are sent in what is called a SOAP envelope that is used\n\r\nas an XML wrapper for data read and generated.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sexta-feira, dia 2/11.'),(671,'Pergunta do dia: 805','1rQphQTpO2E','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-30 09:13:03','What is a left join\n\r\n\r\nA: It returns all rows from the left hand table if there are matches\n\r\nin the right hand side.\n\r\nB: It returns all rows from the left table even if there are no\n\r\nmatches that can be found in the right table.\n\r\nC: It returns some rows from the left hand side.'),(672,'Pergunta do dia: 799','QugXbj2rpIk','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-30 03:17:04','How do you select all the data from the persons table where a city is\n\r\n\r\nA: SELECT * FROM persons WHERE city LIKE \'s%\'\n\r\nB: SELECT city FROM persons WHERE city LIKE \'s%\'\n\r\nC: SELECT * FROM persons WHERE city \'s%\''),(673,'Pergunta do dia: 798','6_d-_9lJri0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-30 09:14:57','Which of the following is a correct way to throw an exception in PHP\n\r\n\r\nA: throw new Exception(\"An exception\");\n\r\nB: $ex = new Exception(\"An exception\");\n\r\nC: throw -&gt; Exception(\"An exception\");'),(674,'Pergunta do dia: 609','8JRLvKtFq1Y','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-29 07:16:51','Como contar um objeto?A: usar Iterator\r\nB: fazer count($obj) ou sizeof($obj)\r\nC: usar ArrayAccess\nObs.: pergunta de terça-feira, dia 17/4.'),(675,'Pergunta do dia: 804','wTzwwuqxMXU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-29 02:02:23','How do you declare an abstract class called data with the methods\n\r\ninsert and close.\n\r\n\r\nA:\n\r\nabstract class data {\n\r\n abstract function insert();\n\r\n abstract function close();\n\r\n}\n\r\n\r\nB:\n\r\nabstract class data {\n\r\n function insert();\n\r\n function close();\n\r\n}\n\r\n\r\nC:\n\r\nclass data abstract {\n\r\n abstract function insert();\n\r\n abstract function close();\n\r\n}'),(676,'Pergunta do dia: 803','psRcvMpJU5Q','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-29 09:33:27','What is the purpose of the Recursive iterator:\n\r\n\r\nA: The recursive iteration allows the ability to loop through a multi\n\r\ndimensional object scructure.\n\r\nB: The recursive iteration allow the ability to loop through a single\n\r\ndimensional array tree data structure.\n\r\nC: The recursive iteration allow the ability to loop through a multi\n\r\ndimensional tree data structure SimpleXML. e.g. xml trees.'),(677,'Pergunta do dia: 802','Ln-bAqjJa-k','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-29 08:54:06','What is the purpose of lazy loading\n\r\n\r\nA: To improve readability of the imported classes.\n\r\nB: Lazy loading is a concept that classes can be loaded on demand.\n\r\nC: Lazy loading is to add classes before they are needed.'),(678,'Pergunta do dia: 801','YOiI0J5D-D0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-26 01:57:52','How do we add a record into customer with first_name John last_name\n\r\nFreg address 48 Willber road phone number 0927 8234115\n\r\n\r\nA: INSERT INTO customer(cust_id, first_name, last_name, address,\n\r\nphonenumber) VALUE (1, John, Freg, 48 Willber road, 0927 8234115);\n\r\nB: INSERT INTO customer(cust_id, first_name, last_name, address,\n\r\nphonenumber) VALUE (1, \'John\', \'Freg\', \'48 Willber road\', \'0927\n\r\n8234115\');\n\r\nC: INSERT customer(cust_id, first_name, last_name, address,\n\r\nphonenumber) VALUE (1, John, Freg, 48 Willber road, 0927 8234115);'),(679,'Pergunta do dia: 800','iZqj8uW_3rw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-25 10:04:57','How do you declare a destructor\n\r\n\r\nA: function __destructor() {}\n\r\nB: fun __destructor() {}\n\r\nC: pub __destructor() {}'),(680,'Pergunta do dia: 796','sCyIEIOa5do','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-22 01:38:13','What is the right definition of session hijacking\n\r\n\r\nA: Processing invalid data as it is the exploitation of a computer bug.\n\r\nB: A web browser generates a random session identifier.\n\r\nC: An attacker gains access to another user\'s session by exploiting\n\r\nPHP session vulnerabilities.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo (dia 21/10).'),(681,'Pergunta do dia: 797','RVJVcF9SQuc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-22 01:37:36','Which of the following explains \"cross-site request forgeries\" correctly\n\r\n\r\nA: An attacker forging an HTTP request from another user by tricking a\n\r\nuser into sending an HTTP request on the attacker\'s behalf.\n\r\nB: Exploits the vulnerability of a system which allows an attacker to\n\r\nset another user\'s session identifier mostly from URL query string(s)\n\r\nor POST data.\n\r\nC: A cracker inserting a malicious SQL statement to be run on your\n\r\ndatabase without your knowledge by exploiting a unescaped SQL\n\r\nstatement.'),(682,'Pergunta do dia: 787','1keTj5qWCzA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-19 09:04:37','You are creating an application that generates invoices in a variety\n\r\nof formats, including PDF, ODS and HTML. Each of these formats is\n\r\nrepresented as a PHP class in your application. While some of the\n\r\noperations can be performed on all of the different formats (such as\n\r\nsaving and loading), other operations may be specific to one or two of\n\r\nthe formats (such as setting as read only). Which design pattern\n\r\nshould you use for this application?\n\r\n\r\nA: Adapter\n\r\nB: Factory\n\r\nC: MVC\n\r\nD: Singleton\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sexta-feira, dia 12/10.'),(683,'Pergunta do dia: 789','D85OPwIYCfY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-19 09:00:05','Which of following is a valid function definition in PHP:\n\r\n\r\nA: int f()\n\r\nB: private int f()\n\r\nC: function f()\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de domingo, dia 14/10.'),(684,'Pergunta do dia: 790','49h4kP68NxE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-19 08:59:32','What is the output of following PHP statements:\n\r\n\r\n$a = 20;\n\r\n$b = $a;\n\r\n$b = 20;\n\r\necho $a\n\r\n\r\nA: 15\n\r\nB: 10\n\r\nC: 20'),(685,'Pergunta do dia: 791','KPln5GV_ERY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-19 08:58:52','Which of the following sets a cookie successfully\n\r\n\r\nA: set_cookie(\"chocolate_cookie\", \"tasty\");\n\r\nB: setcookie(\"chocolate_cookie\", \"tasty\");\n\r\nC: $cookie[\'chocolate_cookie\'] = \'tasty\';'),(686,'Pergunta do dia: 792','DfutzU9m0k0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-19 08:57:36','What is the output of following PHP statements:\n\r\n$x = 1;\n\r\necho $x &lt;&lt; 1;\n\r\n\r\nA: 3\n\r\nB: 2\n\r\nC: 1'),(687,'Pergunta do dia: 793','qHTGWNnVK70','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-19 08:48:58','What is the output of:\n\r\necho (int)2.75;\n\r\n\r\nA: 2.75\n\r\nB: 3\n\r\nC: 2'),(688,'Pergunta do dia: 788','dOFx4gLhjsA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-15 10:43:48','What is the output of following PHP statement:\n\r\necho strspn(\'133445abcdef\',\'12345\');\n\r\n\r\nA: 6\n\r\nB: -1\n\r\nC: 1\n\r\n\r\nObs.: sábado, dia 13/10'),(689,'Pergunta do dia: 786','PR_MJ25vjq8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-15 10:19:37','Which of the following statements is correct?\n\r\n\r\nA: Interfaces can extend only one interface\n\r\nB: Interfaces can extend more than one interface\n\r\nC: Interfaces can inherit a method from different interfaces\n\r\nD: Interfaces can redeclare inherited methods'),(690,'Pergunta do dia: 785','eZ8caoLXpH4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-11 10:23:04','An HTML form contains this form element:\n\r\n&lt;input type=\"image\" name=\"myImage\" src=\"image.png\" /&gt;\n\r\nThe user clicks on the image to submit the form. How can you now\n\r\naccess the relative coordinates of the mouse click?\n\r\n\r\nA: $_IMAGE[\'myImage\'][\'x\'] and $_IMAGE[\'myImage\'][\'y\']\n\r\nB: $_POST[\'myImage\'][\'x\'] and $_POST[\'myImage\'][\'x\']\n\r\nC: $_POST[\'myImage.x\'] and $_POST[\'myImage.y\']\n\r\nD: $_POST[\'myImage_x\'] and $_POST[\'myImage_y\']'),(691,'Pergunta do dia: 784','4zcY5TPzAxw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-10 09:22:29','Which of the following data types cannot be directly manipulated by the client?\n\r\n\r\nA: Cookie Data\n\r\nB: Session Data\n\r\nC: Remote IP Address\n\r\nD: User Agent'),(692,'Pergunta do dia: 783','yVs31kiBMVU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-09 11:47:28','Which piece of code will return the ASCII value of a character?\n\r\n\r\nA: (int)\'t\';\n\r\nB: ord(\'t\');\n\r\nC: to_ascii(\'t\');\n\r\nD: chr(\'t\');'),(693,'Pergunta do dia: 782','aSrQ_R-4vp4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-09 11:46:42','Transactions can be used to:\n\r\n(Choose 2)\n\r\n\r\nA: Recover from errors in case of a power outage or a failure in the\n\r\nSQL connection\n\r\nB: Ensure that the data is properly formatted\n\r\nC: Ensure that either all statements are performed properly, or that\n\r\nnone of them are.\n\r\nD: Recover from user error\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo.'),(694,'Pergunta do dia: 781','moocc5doDms','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-09 11:46:17','What is the output of the following code?\n\r\n&lt;code&gt;\n\r\nclass test {\n\r\npublic $value = 0;\n\r\nfunction test() {\n\r\n$this-&gt;value = 1;\n\r\n}\n\r\nfunction __construct() {\n\r\n$this-&gt;value = 2;\n\r\n}\n\r\n}\n\r\n$object = new test();\n\r\necho $object-&gt;value;\n\r\n\r\nA: 2\n\r\nB: 1\n\r\nC: 0\n\r\nD: 3\n\r\nE: No Output, PHP will generate an error message.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sábado, dia 6/10.'),(695,'Pergunta do dia: 778','Faq-UtNRlPE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-08 03:26:12','When checking whether two English words are pronounced alike, which\n\r\nfunction should be used for the best possible result?\n\r\n\r\nA: levenshtein()\n\r\nB: metaphone()\n\r\nC: similar_text()\n\r\nD: soundex()'),(696,'Pergunta do dia: 777','Wbl-vwvP680','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-08 03:25:31','What is the output of the following code?\n\r\necho 0x33, \' monkeys sit on \', 011, \' trees.\';\n\r\n\r\nA: 33 monkeys sit on 11 trees.\n\r\nB: 51 monkeys sit on 9 trees.\n\r\nC: monkeys sit on trees.\n\r\nD: 0x33 monkeys sit on 011 trees.'),(697,'Pergunta do dia: 775','UAxqdziZjvw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-08 03:23:56','What is the output of the following script?\n\r\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\nclass a\n\r\n{\n\r\npublic $val;\n\r\n}\n\r\nfunction renderVal (a $a)\n\r\n{\n\r\nif ($a) {\n\r\necho $a-&gt;val;\n\r\n}\n\r\n}\n\r\nrenderVal (null);\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: A syntax error in the function declaration line\n\r\nB: An error, because null is not an instance of \'a\'\n\r\nC: Nothing, because a null value is being passed to renderVal()\n\r\nD: NULL\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo.'),(698,'Pergunta do dia: 774','f-b09XthsjU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-08 03:20:26','You analyze the code of a collegue and see, it uses the function\n\r\nstrcasecmp. You try it out to see what it does and use the following\n\r\nfunction call:\n\r\nstrcasecmp(\'hello my dear!\', \'Hello my DEAR!\');\n\r\nThe function call returns \"0\". What does that mean?\n\r\n\r\nA: String 1 is less than string 2.\n\r\nB: The strings are considered equal.\n\r\nC: String 2 is less than string 1.\n\r\nD: The strings have equal length.'),(699,'Pergunta do dia: 780','Nc1rL54qMlg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-08 10:37:23','What is the maximum size of the VARCHAR column type?\n\r\n\r\nA: 255 Bytes\n\r\nB: 255 Characters\n\r\nC: 512 Bytes\n\r\nD: 512 Characters\n\r\nE: No Limit'),(700,'Pergunta do dia: 779','67SKcUy-W7Q','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-10-05 12:41:14','Given the following code, what is correct?\n\r\nfunction f(stdClass &amp;$x = NULL) { $x = 42;\n\r\n}\n\r\n$z = new stdClass;\n\r\nf($z);\n\r\nvar_dump($z);\n\r\n\r\nA: Error: Typehints cannot be NULL\n\r\nB: Error: Typehints cannot be references\n\r\nC: Result is NULL\n\r\nD: Result is object of type stdClass\n\r\nE: Result is 42'),(701,'Pergunta do dia: 773','4rni9Fn2vC4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-29 09:46:54','A script residing at http://example.com/phpcert/cookies.php contains\n\r\nthe following code:\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\nsetcookie(\'name1\', \'value1\', time() + 60*60*24, \'/\');\n\r\nsetcookie(\'name1\', \'value2\');\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\nThe web browser is configured to accept all cookies. How many cookies\n\r\nwill be set by this script?\n\r\n\r\nA: 0\n\r\nB: 1\n\r\nC: 2\n\r\nD: 3'),(702,'Pergunta do dia: 772','Eqd5Hq7qvDM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-28 09:10:34','Which options do you have in PHP to set the expiry date of a session?\n\r\n\r\nA: Set the session.duration directive in php.ini\n\r\nB: Set session cookie expiry date locally via session_set_cookie_params()\n\r\nC: Set session expiry date locally via session_cache_expire()\n\r\nD: None of the above'),(703,'Pergunta do dia: 771','uQtyGcgGfmY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-26 12:13:22','What is the content of $c after the following code has executed?\n\r\n$a = 2;\n\r\n$b = 3;\n\r\n$c = ($a++ * ++$b);\n\r\n\r\nA: 0\n\r\nB: 5\n\r\nC: 8\n\r\nD: 4'),(704,'Pergunta do dia: 770','6F9h0YcVJ1g','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-26 09:38:51','Which of the following data types is implicitly passed by reference in\n\r\nPHP 5 while it is passed by value in PHP 4?\n\r\n\r\nA: Class\n\r\nB: String\n\r\nC: Object\n\r\nD: Array'),(705,'Pergunta do dia: 769','q_wL78EyGUY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-25 03:38:48','What DOMElement method should be used to check for availability of a\n\r\nnon-namespaced attribute?\n\r\n\r\nA: getAttributeNS()\n\r\nB: getAttribute()\n\r\nC: hasAttribute()\n\r\nD: hasAttributeNS()'),(706,'Pergunta do dia: 766','lzHlhIgVuaI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-22 02:39:51','When a class is defined as final it:\n\r\n\r\nA: Can no longer be extended by other classes.\n\r\nB: Means methods in the class are not over-loadable.\n\r\nC: Cannot be defined as such, final is only applicable to object methods.\n\r\nD: Is no longer iteratable.'),(707,'Pergunta do dia: 765','9ZJY_HZDsFc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-21 02:53:22','How many times will the function counter() be executed in the following code?\n\r\nfunction counter($start, &amp;$stop)\n\r\n{\n\r\nif ($stop &gt; $start)\n\r\n{\n\r\nreturn;\n\r\n}\n\r\ncounter($start--, ++$stop);\n\r\n}\n\r\n$start = 5;\n\r\n$stop = 2;\n\r\ncounter($start, $stop);\n\r\n\r\nA: 3\n\r\nB: 4\n\r\nC: 5\n\r\nD: 6'),(708,'Pergunta do dia: 764','By4UkliLf3s','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-20 12:41:00','Identify the security vulnerability in the following example:\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\necho \"Welcome, {$_POST[\'name\']}.\";\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: SQL Injection\n\r\nB: Cross-Site Scripting\n\r\nC: Remote Code Injection\n\r\nD: None of the above'),(709,'Pergunta do dia: 763','ZtCIsy0fxlM','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-20 10:46:48','Which of the following filtering techniques prevents cross-site\n\r\nscripting (XSS) vulnerabilities?\n\r\n\r\nA: Strip all occurrences of the string script.\n\r\nB: Strip all occurrences of the string javascript.\n\r\nC: Enable magic_quotes_gpc.\n\r\nD: None of the above.'),(710,'Pergunta do dia: 761','rMV1RP8u02U','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-19 01:30:26','How many elements does the $matches array contain after the following\n\r\nfunction call is performed?\n\r\npreg_match(\'/^(\\d{1,2}([a-z]+))(?:\\s*)\\S+ (?=200[0-9])/\', \'21st March\n\r\n2006\', $matches);\n\r\n\r\nA: 1\n\r\nB: 2\n\r\nC: 3\n\r\nD: 4\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta do dia 16/9, domingo.'),(711,'Pergunta do dia: 762','T4s_GksyKfk','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-19 10:13:15','Given the following code, what will be the value of $a?\n\r\n$a = array(\'a\', \'b\');\n\r\narray_push($a, array(1, 2));\n\r\n\r\nA: array(\'a\', \'b\', 1, 2)\n\r\nB: array(1, 2, \'a\', \'b\')\n\r\nC: array(array(1, 2), \'a\', \'b\')\n\r\nD: None of the above\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta do dia 17/9, ontem.'),(712,'Pergunta do dia: 760','M_9oJaE_pQE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-19 10:03:59','Type hinting in PHP allows the identification of the following variable types:\n\r\n(Choose 2)\n\r\n\r\nA: String\n\r\nB: Integer\n\r\nC: Array\n\r\nD: Any class or interface type\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta do dia 15/9, sábado.'),(713,'Pergunta do dia: 759','gpcRmpQ9c70','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-19 10:01:19','Which of the following statements is NOT true?\n\r\na) Class constants are public\n\r\nb) Class constants are being inherited\n\r\nc) Class constants can omit initialization (default to NULL)\n\r\nd) Class constants can be initialized by consts\n\r\n\r\nA: a)\n\r\nB: b)\n\r\nC: c)\n\r\nD: d)\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta do dia 14/9, sexta-feira.'),(714,'Pergunta do dia: 758','yvSvQNn07GU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-19 10:00:04','You work for a shared hosting provider, and your supervisor asks you\n\r\nto disable user scripts to dynamically load PHP extensions using the\n\r\ndl() function. How can you do this? (Choose 2)\n\r\n\r\nA: Set enable_dl to Off in the server\'s php.ini configuration file.\n\r\nB: Add dl to the current value of disable_functions in the server\'s\n\r\nphp.ini configuration file.\n\r\nC: Add dl to the current value of disable_classes in the server\'s\n\r\nphp.ini configuration file.\n\r\nD: Write a custom function called dl(), save it under the name\n\r\nprepend.inc and then set the auto_prepend_file directive to\n\r\nprepend.inc in php.ini.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta do dia 13/9, quinta-feira.'),(715,'Pergunta do dia: 686','_Jma2yZaijU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-12 09:26:04','&lt;?php\n\r\n$strings = array(\"@a1\", \"\\n\");\n\r\nforeach($strings as $name =&gt; $testcase) {\n\r\nif((ctype_cntrl($testcase))){\n\r\n        echo \"true\\n\";\n\r\n        }\n\r\n        else {\n\r\n        echo \"false\\n\";\n\r\n        }\n\r\n}\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: true\n\r\ntrue\n\r\nB: true\n\r\nfalse\n\r\nC: false\n\r\nfalse\n\r\nD: false\n\r\ntrue'),(716,'Pergunta do dia: 607','BThqkWwBMj8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-12 08:03:45','Observe as cláusulas SQL em PDO:\r\n$db-&gt;exec(\"INSERT INTO tab VALUES (\'Bill\')\");\r\n$db-&gt;beginTransaction();\r\n$db-&gt;exec(\"INSERT INTO tab VALUES (\'John\')\");A: as duas querys foram executadas\r\nB: só \"Bill\" foi inserido\r\nC: só \"John\" foi inserido\nObs.: pergunta de domingo, dia 15/4.'),(717,'Pergunta do dia: 756','H72bJy45DZY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-11 10:32:51','What does the private visibility modifier do?\n\r\n\r\nA: Allows the variable or function to be visible to the current class\n\r\nand classes that inherit this class.\n\r\nB: Allows the variable or function to be visible inside and outside the class.\n\r\nC: This means that the variable or function is only visible within the\n\r\ncurrent class.'),(718,'Pergunta do dia: 755','2ysqKEH6sw8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-10 10:27:25','Which of the following are valid ways of adding a variable string\n\r\nvalue to an existing string?\n\r\n\r\nA: $sentance = \"Jane went to the \" . $place;\n\r\n\r\nB: $sentance = \'Jane went to the $place\';\n\r\n\r\nC: $sentance = \"Jane went to the $place\";\n\r\n\r\nD: $sentance = \"Jane went to the \";\n\r\n$sentance .= $place;\n\r\n\r\nE: $sentance = sprintf(\"Jane went to the %s\", $place);'),(719,'Pergunta do dia: 752','BxuguOthj7o','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-10 08:49:05','Which is a valid input parameter to the following function?\n\r\nfunction SetSpeed(Speed speed = null)\n\r\n{\n\r\n\r\n}\n\r\n\r\nA: SetSpeed(70);\n\r\nB: SetSpeed(new Speed(70));\n\r\nC: SetSpeed(\'70\');\n\r\nD: SetSpeed(null);'),(720,'Pergunta do dia: 619','1q3QdBRABio','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:52:18','Como obter o formato \"2012-03-30 13:42:57\" de data e horário através\n\r\nda classe DateTime?\n\r\n\r\nA: $date-&gt;format(\'Y-m-d H:i:s\');\n\r\nB: date_format($date, \'Y-m-d H:i:s\');\n\r\nC: date(\'Y-m-d H:i:s\', $timestamp);\n\r\n\r\nObs.: essa é a pergunta de sexta-feria.\n\r\nPulei para o número 619 pois as perguntas novas vieram com numeração repetida.\n\r\n\r\nAbs.\n\r\nAri Jr.'),(721,'Pergunta do dia: 611','ty2a_UtXaQc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:49:21','Quantas vezes a função count foi executada:\r\n&lt;?php\r\nfunction count($a, &amp;$b) {\r\n       if($a &gt; $b) {\r\n               count($a--, ++$b);\r\n               return;\r\n       }\r\n}\r\n$a = 5;\r\n$b = 2;\r\ncount($a, $b);\r\n?&gt;Campo aberto.\nObs.: pergunta de quinta-feira, dia 19/4.'),(722,'Pergunta do dia: 713','EBLRsGx6QLg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:24:23','Which of the following provides NO significant protection from SQL Injection?\n\r\n\r\nA: Validate all incoming data\n\r\nB: Strip common SQL commands\n\r\nC: Using prepared statements\n\r\nD: Using database-specific escaping-functions'),(723,'Pergunta do dia: 714','-5DU9mbfVtQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:23:14','When using PHP with shared hosting, where should you store your\n\r\nsession information?\n\r\n\r\nA: In the htdocs\n\r\nB: In the /tmp folder\n\r\nC: In a folder PHP does not have write access to\n\r\nD: If a folder only the current user has read access to'),(724,'Pergunta do dia: 697','f6Qlhhvd7Zc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:22:43','What function can be use to create your own streams using the PHP\n\r\nstream wrapper and register them within PHP?\n\r\n\r\nA: stream_wrapper_reg\n\r\nB: stream_wrapper\n\r\nC: stream_wrapper_register\n\r\nD: wrapper_register\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sábado, dia 14/7.'),(725,'Pergunta do dia: 710','3PE5nTvLwQY','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:06:36','The function which returns an array of all defined variables is __________ .\n\r\n\r\nA: get_defined_vars()\n\r\nB: get_vars()\n\r\nC: get_defined_vars_array()\n\r\nD: get_vars_array()\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sexta-feira, dia 27/7.'),(726,'Pergunta do dia: 715','3f-xR8oEwCg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:05:23','Which of the following characters are NOT escaped by escapeshellarg()?\n\r\n(choose 2)\n\r\n\r\nA: &amp;\n\r\nB: \"\n\r\nC: \'\n\r\nD: ;'),(727,'Pergunta do dia: 718','m38LjIUz3w0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:04:47','The function which will deletes a file is _________ .\n\r\n\r\nA: file_delete()\n\r\nB: fdelete()\n\r\nC: unlink()\n\r\nD: file_unlink()'),(728,'Pergunta do dia: 719','_WRxZYxxmOQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:04:29','fputcsv() function  will _________ .\n\r\n\r\nA: Format line as CSV and write to file pointer.\n\r\nB: Parses a line from an open file, checking for CSV fields.\n\r\nC: Only gets the contents from an open file.\n\r\nD: Only puts the content to a file.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo (dia 5/8).'),(729,'Pergunta do dia: 727','1CKJX0QOTWA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 08:00:20','The left associative dot operator (.) is used in PHP for:\n\r\n\r\nA: multiplication\n\r\nB: concatenation\n\r\nC: separate object and its member\n\r\nD: delimeter'),(730,'Pergunta do dia: 726','oOC7O3eB3_w','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 07:57:56','Which encryption is recommended if your application needs to store\n\r\ndatabase credentials?\n\r\n\r\nA: Symmetric-key encryption\n\r\nB: Hashing\n\r\nC: Ceasar cipher\n\r\nD: ROT13\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo.'),(731,'Pergunta do dia: 732','vrXuBRVc2ek','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-09 07:57:17','What is a recursive user defined function?\n\r\n\r\nA: A recursive function is a function that uses a for loop to loop\n\r\naround its internal code\n\r\nB: A recursive function is a function that calls itself\n\r\nC: A recursive function stores itself in a serialised file\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, sábado (dia 18/8).'),(732,'Pergunta do dia: 742','GjYOEm3wBz8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-08 08:52:59','Why use the __get method do?\n\r\n\r\nA: The __get method gets a clone of the class.\n\r\nB: The __get method gets a string representation of the class.\n\r\nC: The _get method gets the value of a variable of the class.'),(733,'Pergunta do dia: 740','PuyojDm-u5w','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-08 08:51:59','A do-while loop is a...\n\r\n\r\nA: A infinite loop\n\r\nB: Loops until some condition is met\n\r\nC: Is a finite loop\n\r\nD: Performs the condition test before looping\n\r\nE: Performs the condition test after looping\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo (dia 26/8).'),(734,'Pergunta do dia: 696','PpKo53Fvg2M','Felipe Barth','2012-09-08 05:50:00','What is the output of the following PHP script?\r\n&lt;?php\r\n    $numbers = array(5, 6, 7, 8);\r\n    end($numbers);\r\n\r\n    while (key($numbers)) {\r\n        echo current($numbers);\r\n        prev($numbers);\r\n    }\r\n?&gt;\r\nSelect 1 answer\r\nA) 0123\r\nB) 8765\r\nC) 012\r\nD) 876'),(735,'Pergunta do dia: 698','QqjOSqaObns','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-07 09:19:29','What is the main reason for adding indexes to tables?\n\r\n\r\nA: Only indexed columns may be used in expressions\n\r\nB: Indexes enforce referential integrity\n\r\nC: Indexes can speed up execution of queries\n\r\nD: Indexes can speed up table maintenance tasks\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de domingo, dia 15/7.'),(736,'Pergunta do dia: 702','KeOjIu574uU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-07 08:21:15','Constans are allways _________________ .\n\r\n\r\nA: private\n\r\nB: protected\n\r\nC: public\n\r\nD: undefined\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem.'),(737,'Pergunta do dia: 701','NFqgTDIP6bI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-07 07:19:20','A class cannot implement two interfaces that share function names.\n\r\n\r\nA: true\n\r\nB: false'),(738,'Pergunta do dia: 707','kFyn_prNqCQ','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-07 04:14:40','What will be the output of the following script?\n\r\n&lt;?php\n\r\nprint_r(pathinfo(\"/PHPQns/test.txt\", PATHINFO_BASENAME));\n\r\n?&gt;\n\r\n\r\nA: Array ( [basename] =&gt; test.txt )\n\r\nB: Array ( [dirname] =&gt; /PHPQns [basename] =&gt; test.txt [extension] =&gt;\n\r\ntxt [filename] =&gt; test )\n\r\nC: test.txt\n\r\nD: Array ( [basename] =&gt; test.txt [extension] =&gt; txt )'),(739,'Pergunta do dia: 717','rcobG7p2M0M','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-07 02:08:53','The function opens a process file pointer is __________ . The function\n\r\nfor closes it is _______ .\n\r\n\r\nA: fopen(), fclose()\n\r\nB: proc_open(), proc_close()\n\r\nC: popen(), pclose()\n\r\nD: file_open(), file_close()'),(740,'Pergunta do dia: 751','ttjIF9k8wRw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-06 01:17:56','What does the protected visibility modifier do?\n\r\n\r\nA: Allows the variable or function to be visible to the current class\n\r\nand classes that inherit this class.\n\r\nB: Allows the variable or function to be visible inside and outside the class.\n\r\nC: This means that the variable or function is only visible within the\n\r\ncurrent class.'),(741,'Pergunta do dia: 746','bZN504o7KCA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-06 11:27:52','A foreach loop is a...\n\r\n\r\nA: Finite loop\n\r\nB: Uses a counter variable as part of its strucure\n\r\nC: Reads every element in a array\n\r\nD: A infinite loop\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sábado, dia 1/9.'),(742,'Pergunta do dia: 739','CSM0q9J4D3c','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-05 09:22:37','Why use an Interface?\n\r\n\r\nA: This displays the information on the web page.\n\r\nB: To enable PHP to implement more than one interface rather than\n\r\nallowing other options like multiple inheritance.\n\r\nC: To provide a contract that the class must implement.\n\r\nD: An interface can be used as an alternative to inheritance.'),(743,'Pergunta do dia: 750','netm9YMi7Ww','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-09-05 01:54:37','What functions does a class have to implement when