\r\n$d = \"b\";\n\r\n\r\nA: echo $a;\n\r\nB: echo {\"a\"};\n\r\nC: echo $b;\n\r\nD: echo {$c.$d};\n\r\nE: echo {\"ab\"};\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de sexta-feira, dia 17/8.'),(749,'Pergunta do dia: 743','LSJEnbW8jLo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-08-29 04:33:19','What is an abstract class?\n\r\n\r\nA: A class that another class can implement\n\r\nB: A class that another class can extend\n\r\nC: A class that can\'t be instantiated\n\r\nD: A class that can be instantiated'),(750,'Pergunta do dia: 741','HZWUMsjSiZc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-08-27 01:39:47','What does a try..catch block do?\n\r\n\r\nA: Catches all errors within the try part of the try..catch block\n\r\nB: Catches any exceptions within the try part of the try..catch block\n\r\nC: Supresses exceptions within the try part of the try..catch block\n\r\nand allows those errors to be handled in the catch part of the\n\r\ntry..catch block'),(751,'Pergunta do dia: 738','G-dlQB6g5-8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-08-27 09:24:19','When a variable is passed to a function what is the first thing that\n\r\nshould be done to that variable?\n\r\n\r\nA: The variable should be tested for being null.\n\r\nB: The size of the variable should be tested.\n\r\nC: The variable should be tested to ensure it is the correct type.\n\r\n\r\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, sexta-feira (dia 24/8).'),(752,'Pergunta do dia: 737','HF-qQvVOkV8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-08-23 10:10:08','What of the following statements are true about the foreach loop?\n\r\n\r\nA: The foreach loop, iterates through only the keys of an array.\n\r\nB: The foreach loop iterates through all the items in a array.\n\r\nC: The foreach loop is a finite loop.\n\r\nD: The foreach loop is a infinite loop.'),(753,'Pergunta do dia: 735','v1YC7ZB7MpA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2012-08-23 09:36:04','What does the @ operator do?\n\r\n\r\nA: Increments the value it is in front of.\n\r\nB: Decrements the value it is in front of.\n\r\nC: Re-runs the function it was in front o