rect() function\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, sexta-feira.'),(995,'Pergunta do dia: 464','TQwYafw4BcU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-24 09:54:43','Which of the following functions are used with the internal array\r\npointer to accomplish an action?\r\n(choose 4)A: key\r\nB: forward\r\nC: prev\r\nD: current\r\nE: next'),(996,'Pergunta do dia: 462','2VoMzP5kvb8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-23 09:34:56','What is wrong with the following code valid in PHP 4 but invalid in PHP 5?&lt;?php\r\nclass MyClass {\r\nfunction reassign($var) {\r\n$this = $var;\r\n}\r\n}\r\n$a = new MyClass();\r\n$b = new MyClass();\r\n$a-&gt;reassign($b);\r\n?&gt;\nA: Reassigning $this in PHP 5 throws a fatal error\r\nB: It is missing access restrictions (public,private,protected)\r\nrequired in PHP 5\r\nC: Classes need to implement the OverLoad interface for this behavior in PHP 5\r\nD: $b is now an object handle and the reassign() method needs to be\r\ndeclared pass-by-reference'),(997,'Pergunta do dia: 461','m5LXx5XKXuo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-22 09:31:24','What is the best way to iterate and modify every element of an array\r\nusing PHP 5?A: You cannot modify an array during iteration\nB: for($i = 0; $i &lt; count($array);\r\n$i++) { /* ... */ }\nC: foreach($array as $key =&gt;\r\n&amp;$val) { /* ... */ }\nD: foreach($array as $key =&gt; $val)\r\n{ /* ... */ }\nE: while(list($key, $val) =\r\neach($array)) { /* ... */'),(998,'Pergunta do dia: 460','el4RroVMm1E','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-20 08:58:27','SimpleXML objects can be created from what types of data sources?\r\n(choose 3)A: A String\r\nB: An array\r\nC: A DomDocument object\r\nD: A URI\r\nE: A Database resource'),(999,'Pergunta do dia: 459','uc8hKWWhgd0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-19 08:57:50','Which php.ini directive should be disabled to prevent the execution of\r\na remote PHP script via an include or require construct?A: You cannot disable remote PHP script execution\r\nB: curl.enabled\r\nC: allow_remote_url\r\nD: allow_url_fopen\r\nE: allow_require'),(1000,'Pergunta do dia: 458','Rn0h200HUlU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-18 09:20:59','How can you modify the copy of an object during a clone operation?A: Put the logic in the object\'s constructor to alter the values\r\nB: Implement your own function to do object copying\r\nC: Implement the object\'s __clone() method\r\nD: Implement __get() and __set() methods with the correct logic\r\nE: Implement the __copy() method with the correct logic'),(1001,'Pergunta do dia: 457','dKGYU1Zk_MI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-18 09:14:52','In PHP 5\'s object model, a class can have multiple ______ but only a\r\nsingle direct ________.A: None of the above\r\nB: interfaces, child\r\nC: children, interface\r\nD: interfaces, parent\r\nE: parents, interface'),(1002,'Pergunta do dia: 452','CKa82Q4b4ds','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-16 12:11:29','Which of the following list of potential data sources should be\r\nconsidered trusted?A: None of the above\r\nB: $_ENV\r\nC: $_GET\r\nD: $_COOKIE\r\nE: $_SERVER\nObs.: essa é de sábado.'),(1003,'Pergunta do dia: 455','4PPNOq6gjPk','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-16 11:22:40','Consider the following example XML document:\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"ISO-8859-1\" ?&gt;\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\r\n\"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\"&gt;\r\n&lt;html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n&lt;title&gt;XML Example&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nMoved to &lt;&lt;a\r\nhref=\"http://example.org/\"&gt;http://www.ex\r\nample.org/&lt;/a&gt;.&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;What is wrong with this document, and how can\r\nit be corrected?\n(choose 2)\r\nA: The document is completely valid\r\nB: All special XML characters must be represented as entities within\r\nthe content of a node\r\nC: All tags must be closed\r\nD: You cannot specify a namespace for the &lt;html&gt; attribute\r\nE: The DOCTYPE declaration is malformed'),(1004,'Pergunta do dia: 454','13l-x1PMc9g','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-16 11:05:20','Setting a cookie on the client in PHP 5 can be best accomplished by:A: Use the add_cookie() function\r\nB: Use the setcookie() function\r\nC: Use the the apache_send_header() function\r\nD: Setting a variable in the $_COOKIE\r\nE: superglobal'),(1005,'Pergunta do dia: 453','GxYcx4RfGgI','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-16 11:04:33','The _____ keyword is used to block any overriding of a class/method by\r\na subclass.A: static\r\nB: None of the above\r\nC: protected\r\nD: final\r\nE: private\nObs.: essa é de ontem (domingo).'),(1006,'Pergunta do dia: 451','ZegJCq8C3DE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-16 11:02:20','What is the output of the following\r\ncode?\r\n&lt;?php\r\nfunction\r\nbyReference(&amp;$variable = 5)\r\n{\r\necho ++$variable;\r\n}\r\nbyReference();\r\n?&gt;A: No output or error. Variables can not be optional and passed by reference.\r\nB: 5\r\nC: 6\nObs.: essa é de sexta-feira. Lamento pelo atraso...'),(1007,'Pergunta do dia: 456','JaVJI2rrK04','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-16 11:01:45','Unlike a database such as MySQL, SQLite columns are not explicitly\r\ntyped. Instead, SQLite catagorizes data into which of the following\r\ncatagories?\r\n(choose 2)A: textual\r\nB: unicode\r\nC: numeric\r\nD: binary\r\nE: constant'),(1008,'Pergunta do dia: 449','oi_odhlRop8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-11 02:39:36','In PHP 4 you could iterate over every member property of an object\r\nusing foreach(), in PHP 5 to accomplish the same task on a non-public\r\narray you could use the ___________ interface.'),(1009,'Pergunta do dia: 450','5-8IIWI3_v8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-10 09:45:20','What is the output of the following script?&lt;?php\nclass A {\n  public function bar() {\r\n    print \"Hello\";\r\n  }\n}\nclass B extends A {\n  function bar() {\r\n    print \"Goodbye\";\r\n  }\r\n}\n$c = new B();\r\n$c-&gt;bar();\r\n?&gt;'),(1010,'Pergunta do dia: 448','ddCbgmxuCjc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-08 02:26:06','The method used to create a new node to be added into an XML document\r\nusing DOM is the ___________ method.'),(1011,'Pergunta do dia: 445','bv61m9dOP-g','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-08 08:35:33','What combination of boolean values for $a, $b, $c, and $d will result\r\nin the variable $number being equal to 3?&lt;?php\r\n$a = null;\r\n$b = null;\r\n$c = null;\r\n$d = null;\nif($a &amp;&amp; !$b) {\r\n  if(!!$c &amp;&amp; !$d) {\r\n    if($d &amp;&amp; ($a || $c)) {\r\n      if(!$d &amp;&amp; $b) {\r\n        $number = 1;\r\n      } else {\r\n        $number = 2;\r\n      }\r\n    } else {\r\n      $number = 3;\r\n    }\r\n  } else {\r\n    $number = 4;\r\n  }\r\n} else {\r\n  $number = 5;\r\n}\r\n?&gt;\nA: false, true, true, true\r\nB: true, false, true, false\r\nC: true, true, false, false\r\nD: false, true, true, false\r\nE: false, false, true, false'),(1012,'Pergunta do dia: 447','Anboau0biU0','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-07 05:40:28','The _________ method can be used from a SimpleXML node to return an\r\niterator containing a list of all of the current node\'s subnodes.'),(1013,'Pergunta do dia: 446','v4rewUEXcgU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-07 04:09:00','The _______ function is used to convert an array into a string,\r\nmaintaining your ability to return the string into an array.Obs.: de ontem (domingo). Pergunta de campo aberto...'),(1014,'Pergunta do dia: 444','KZmGdEw5xyk','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-04 10:08:48','Which of the following functions could be used to break a string into an array?\r\n(choose 3)A: array_split()\r\nB: split()\r\nC: string_split()\r\nD: preg_match_all()\r\nE: explode()'),(1015,'Pergunta do dia: 442','3_bVvrzndig','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-03 07:19:25','What is the best approach for converting this string:$string = \"a=10&amp;b[]=20&amp;c=30&amp;d=40+50\";\nInto this array?\narray(4) {\r\n  [\"a\"]=&gt;\r\n  string(2) \"10\"\r\n  [\"b\"]=&gt;\r\n  array(1) {\r\n    [0]=&gt;\r\n    string(2) \"20\"\r\n  }\r\n  [\"c\"]=&gt;\r\n  string(2) \"30\"\r\n  [\"d\"]=&gt;\r\n  string(5) \"40 50\"\r\n}\nA: Write a parser completely by hand, it\'s the only way to make sure\r\nit\'s 100% accurate\r\nB: Use the parse_str() function to translate it to an array()\r\nC: Pass the variable to another PHP script via an HTTP GET request and\r\nreturn the array as a serialized variable\r\nD: Just call unserialize() to translate it to an array()\r\nE: Write a string parser using strtok() and unserialize() to convert\r\nit to an array'),(1016,'Pergunta do dia: 441','TGtePlxJUGs','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-11-03 09:12:50','What is the output of the following code?&lt;?php\nclass MyException extends Exception {}\r\nclass AnotherException extends MyException {}\nclass Foo {\r\n  public function something() {\r\n    throw new AnotherException();\r\n  }\r\n  public function somethingElse() {\r\n    throw new MyException();\r\n  }\r\n}\n$a = new Foo();\ntry {\r\n  try {\r\n    $a-&gt;something();        \r\n  } catch(AnotherException $e) {\r\n    $a-&gt;somethingElse();        \r\n  } catch(MyException $e) {\r\n    print \"Caught Exception\";\r\n  }\r\n} catch(Exception $e) {\r\n  print \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\";\r\n}\n?&gt;\nA: \"Caught Exception\" followed by \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\"\r\nB: A fatal error for an uncaught exception\r\nC: \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\"\r\nD: \"Didn\'t catch the Exception!\" followed by a fatal error\r\nE: \"Caught Exception\"'),(1017,'Pergunta do dia: 439','t4ed-JsG3Oo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-31 12:53:27','What reproduces the same behavior in PHP 5 as the following PHP 4 code snippet:&lt;?php\r\n$a = new Foo();\r\n$b = $a;\r\n?&gt;\r\n        \r\nA: $b must be copied to $a completely using the clone operator\r\nB: The code remains unchanged in both PHP 4 and PHP 5\r\nC: Set $b to a new instance of the Foo Class\r\nD: This code throws a fatal error in PHP 5\r\nE: $a must be copied using the clone operatior, and $a must be copied\r\ncompletely to $b using the clone operator'),(1018,'Pergunta do dia: 440','86ZTuItLnzg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-31 11:29:02','When working with SimpleXML in PHP 5, the four basic rules on how the\r\nXML document is accessed are which of the following?\r\n(choose 4)A: Element namespaces are denoted by the \'namespace\' attribute\r\nB: converting an element to a string denotes text data\r\nC: Non-numeric indexes are element attributes\r\nD: Numeric indexes are elements\r\nE: Properties denote element iterators'),(1019,'Pergunta do dia: 438','-iHsoOYgbKg','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-31 08:40:58','Which two internal PHP interfaces provide functionality which allow\r\nyou to treat an object like an array?\r\n(choose 2)A: iteration\r\nB: arrayaccess\r\nC: objectarray\r\nD: iterator\r\nE: array\nObs.: essa é a pergunta de ontem, sábado.'),(1020,'Pergunta do dia: 437','sKIVpZv5NBA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-28 10:31:44','To destroy a PHP session completely, one must which of the following?        \r\n(choose 2)A: Regenerate the session ID using session_regenerate_id()\r\nB: If cookies are used, destroy it\r\nC: Use session_demolish() to completely destroy the session\r\nD: Change the session name using session_name()\r\nE: Destroy the session data using session_destroy()'),(1021,'Pergunta do dia: 436','JThyzA5jkwA','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-27 07:36:27','What is the best way to ensure the distinction between filtered /\r\ntrusted and unfiltered / untrusted data?A: None of the above\r\nB: Never trust any data from the user\r\nC: Enable built-in security features such as magic_quotes_gpc and safe_mode\r\nD: Always filter all incoming data\r\nE: Use PHP 5\'s tainted mode'),(1022,'Pergunta do dia: 435','CAajkrnUEN4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-27 08:12:57','The following is an example of what design pattern?&lt;?php\nclass MyClassBuilder {\n  public function build() {\r\n    return new MyClass();\r\n  }\n}\r\n?&gt;\nA: None of the above\r\nB: Builder\r\nC: Factory\r\nD: Singleton\r\nE: Observer'),(1023,'Pergunta do dia: 434','ltcSQpC7GP8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-25 07:27:24','Given the following XML document in a SimpleXML object:&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"ISO-8859-1\" ?&gt;\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html\r\n     PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\r\n     \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\"&gt;\r\n&lt;html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"&gt;\r\n  &lt;head&gt;\r\n    &lt;title&gt;XML Example&lt;/title&gt;\r\n  &lt;/head&gt;\r\n  &lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;\r\n      Moved to &amp;lt;&lt;a\r\nhref=\"http://example.org/\"&gt;http://www.example.org/&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;gt;\r\n      &lt;br/&gt;\r\n    &lt;/p&gt;\r\n  &lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\nSelect the proper statement below which will display the HREF\r\nattribute of the anchor tag.\nA: $sxe-&gt;body-&gt;p[0]-&gt;a[1][\'href\']\r\nB: $sxe-&gt;body-&gt;p-&gt;a-&gt;href\r\nC: $sxe-&gt;body-&gt;p-&gt;a[\'href\']\r\nD: $sxe[\'body\'][\'p\'][0][\'a\'][\'href\']\r\nE: $sxe-&gt;body-&gt;p[1]-&gt;a[\'href\']'),(1024,'Pergunta do dia: 433','aBRTLIrC3DE','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-24 05:03:38','What is the output of the following?&lt;?php\r\nfunction 1dotEach($n)\r\n{\r\n  if ($n &gt; 0)\r\n  {\r\n    1dotEach(--$n);\r\n    echo \".\";\r\n  }else\r\n  {\r\n    return $n;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n1dotEach(4);\r\n?&gt;\n        \r\nA: ...\r\nB: ...0\r\nC: Parse Error: Syntax Error\r\nD: .....\r\nE: ....\r\nF: …'),(1025,'Pergunta do dia: 431','yfjONiqLEDo','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-24 09:23:35','When checking to see if two variables contain the same instance of an\r\nobject, which of the following comparisons should be used?A: if($obj1-&gt;equals($obj2) &amp;&amp; ($obj1 instanceof $obj2))\r\nB: if($obj1-&gt;equals($obj2))\r\nC: if($obj1 === $obj2)\r\nD: if($obj1 instanceof $obj2)\r\nE: if($obj1 == $obj2)'),(1026,'Pergunta do dia: 432','mxW-S2c18z4','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-24 09:16:48','Type-hinting and the instanceof keyword can be used to check what\r\ntypes of things about variables?\r\n(choose 3)A: If a particular child class extends from it\r\nB: If they are an instance of a particular interface\r\nC: If they are an abstract class\r\nD: If they have a particular parent class\r\nE: If they are an instance of a particular class\nObs.: pergunta de ontem, domingo.'),(1027,'Pergunta do dia: 430','sVdQK2GnnWc','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-21 08:20:05','What is the output of the following code?&lt;?php\r\nfunction functionSplit()\r\n{\r\n  $pre = 1;\r\n?&gt;\n&lt;?php\r\n  echo $pre;\r\n}\r\nfunctionSplit();\r\n?&gt;\nA: Error; function declarations can not be split over multiple PHP segments.\r\nB: Nothing\r\nC: 1\r\nD: 2'),(1028,'Pergunta do dia: 429','_L5fp83x-lw','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-20 04:47:33','SQL Injections can be best prevented using which of the following\r\ndatabase technologies?\r\n(choose 1)A: All of the above\r\nB: Prepared Statements\r\nC: Persistent Connections\r\nD: Unbuffered Queries\r\nE: Query escaping'),(1029,'Pergunta do dia: 428','CP4EwAiQaQ8','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-20 02:42:39','Which of the following is the best way to split a string on the \"-=-\" pattern?A: They all are equally proper methods\r\nB: str_split($string, strpos($string, \"-=-\"))\r\nC: preg_split(\"-=-\", $string);\r\nD: explode(\"-=-\" $string);'),(1030,'Pergunta do dia: 425','Sim0X8NyHPU','Ari Stopassola Junior','2011-10-19 09:44:38','Consider the following code:&lt;?php\r\nheader(\"Location: {$_GET[\'url\']}\");\r\n?&gt;\nWhich of the following values of $_GET[\'url\'] would cause session fixation?\r\n(choose 1)\r\nA: Session Fixation is not possible with this code snippet\r\nB: http://www.zend.com/?PHPSESSID=123\r\nC: PHPSESSID%611243\r\nD: Set-Cookie%3A+